------------------
ChuGUI VERSIONS log
------------------

v0.1.3 (November 2025)
=======
(added) ImGUI debug panel for real-time style editing:
 - ChuGUI.debugEnabled(int) -- enable/disable the debug panel
 - ChuGUI.debugAdd() -- add the last rendered component to the debug panel
 - ChuGUI.debug() -- render the debug panel (call each frame)
(added) Support for icon wrap options:
 - UIStyle.VAR_ICON_WRAP -- sets all wrap axes at once; options are TextureSampler.Wrap_Repeat, TextureSampler.Wrap_Mirror, or TextureSampler.Wrap_Clamp
 - UIStyle.VAR_ICON_WRAP_U -- options are TextureSampler.Wrap_Repeat, TextureSampler.Wrap_Mirror, or TextureSampler.Wrap_Clamp
 - UIStyle.VAR_ICON_WRAP_V -- options are TextureSampler.Wrap_Repeat, TextureSampler.Wrap_Mirror, or TextureSampler.Wrap_Clamp
 - UIStyle.VAR_ICON_WRAP_W -- options are TextureSampler.Wrap_Repeat, TextureSampler.Wrap_Mirror, or TextureSampler.Wrap_Clamp
(added) Support for rect transparency:
 - UIStyle.VAR_RECT_TRANSPARENT
(added) ChuGUI.worldToNDCSize(vec2 worldSize)
(added) Component size variables now respect the ChuGUI.units() setting.
(added) ChuGUI.sizeUnits(string unit) -- set the unit system for sizes only (ChuGUI.NDC or ChuGUI.WORLD).
(added) ChuGUI.posUnits(string unit) -- set the unit system for positions only (ChuGUI.NDC or ChuGUI.WORLD).
(changed) ChuGUI.units() now sets both sizeUnits and posUnits.
(added) MouseState support for Rect component.
(fixed) Button text sizing.
(fixed) Fixed/improved Dropdown spacing.
(fixed) Cursor state now only tracks active (rendered) components.

v0.1.2 (November 2025)
=======
(added) Spinner component.
(added) Support for icon transparency and sampler options:
 - UIStyle.VAR_ICON_TRANSPARENT -- options are true/1 or false/0
 - UIStyle.VAR_ICON_SAMPLER -- options are UIStyle.NEAREST or UIStyle.LINEAR
(fixed) Fixed rare modulo-by-zero error that appears when fps drops.
(fixed) When disabled, buttons used to still be clickable.
(fixed) Fixed asset paths for the Checkbox component and examples.
(fixed) Made default styling more consistent.
(removed) Removed UIStyle.COL_COLOR_PICKER_LABEL -- use UIStyle.COL_LABEL instead.

v0.1.1 (October 2025)
=======
(added) ChuGUI.units(string unit), which sets the unit system for the position of components.
(added) ChuGUI.NDC and ChuGUI.WORLD enums to be used with ChuGUI.units(string unit).
(added) Support for label wrapping:
 - UIStyle.VAR_LABEL_ALIGN
 - UIStyle.VAR_LABEL_CHARACTERS
 - UIStyle.VAR_LABEL_MAX_WIDTH
(added) UIStyle.LEFT, UIStyle.CENTER, and UIStyle.RIGHT to be used with UIStyle.VAR_LABEL_ALIGN and UIStyle.VAR_BUTTON_ICON_POSITION.

v0.1.0
=======
Initial Release